{"parentUuid":"d0cf69ed-e31d-4c1a-9bcc-027ba3703490","isSidechain":false,"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Base directory for this skill: /Users/mattupham/.claude/skills/ticket\n\nWork on this Linear ticket end-to-end:\n\nhttps://linear.app/mattupham/issue/MATT-128/phase-0-repo-alignment-src-biome-husky\n\nFollow these steps in order:\n\n**Step 1 — Plan**\nUse the `mcp__linear-server__get_issue` tool (or research the ticket via its URL) to read the full ticket description, acceptance criteria, and any linked context. Then produce a detailed implementation plan: which files to touch, what changes to make, and why. Share the plan and confirm with me before writing any code.\n\n**Step 2 — Implement**\nImplement exactly what the ticket asks. Follow CLAUDE.md and AGENTS.md conventions (no `any`, path aliases, soft deletes, `PlanetScaleDatabase`, etc.). Run `pnpm format` after changes. Add or update tests where behaviour changes.\n\n**Step 3 — Push & PR**\nRun `pnpm check` to verify everything passes. Commit the work, push the branch, and open a pull request using `gh pr create`. Fill out the PR template fully — summary bullets, test plan, and link back to the Linear ticket.\n\n**Step 4 — Review**\nRun `/review` on the PR you just opened.\n\n**Step 5 — Address feedback**\nAddress every piece of feedback from the review — including non-blockers and nits. Push the fixes."}]},"isMeta":true,"uuid":"c117e8f3-69d1-49ff-9783-97cdb907d3d4","timestamp":"2026-04-18T18:27:48.970Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/mattupham/Projects/h2-frontend/.claude/worktrees/matt+matt-128-phase-0-repo-alignment-src-biome-husky","sessionId":"bc695761-c76c-4345-802a-fc47192e3654","version":"2.1.114","gitBranch":"worktree-matt+matt-128-phase-0-repo-alignment-src-biome-husky"}
